headline: Regions Financial: Preferred Shares Offer An Attractive Risk/Reward Ratio
summary: Regions Financial's Series E preferred shares offer a compelling 6.44% yield, well-covered by earnings, and are unlikely to be called soon. Read the full RF stock analysis here.
